<st>
Junction tree algorithm</st>


<ss1>
<st>
Hugin algorithm</st>

<p>

<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../451/4855451.xml">
Moralize</link> the graph</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Introduce the evidence</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

<link>
Triangulate</link> the graph</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Construct a junction tree from this (form a maximal <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../932/456932.xml">
spanning tree</link>)</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Propagate the probabilities (via <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../010/800010.xml">
belief propagation</link>)</entry>
</list>
</p>

